 a creative and multi-talented team comprised of web designers and web developers.&nbsp;BWEBS offers customer-oriented services and delivers creative and effective results.</p><p>&nbsp;<br></p>\n<p><strong>What we offer</strong></p>\n<img src=\"http://bwebssvg.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/banner-web-design-e1511277546461-752x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"Website design &amp; Development\">\n<p>Website Design &amp; Development</p>\n<img src=\"http://bwebssvg.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/we-mobile-app-e1511277456953.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"Web &amp; Mobile Application Development\">\n<p>Web &amp; Mobile Application Development</p>\n<img src=\"http://bwebssvg.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/support-500x288.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"website maintenance and support\">\n<p>Website Maintenance &amp; Support</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">For a WordPress site development project, <strong>BWEBS\'s</strong> typical stages include:</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Planning</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Implementation</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Testing</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Review</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Client training</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Content upload</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Soft launch (and launch)</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Post-launch support and maintenance</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"http://bwebssvg.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Waterfall-Model-2-400x294.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Waterfall-Model-2\">\n'),(136,65,'_edit_lock','1499111085:1'),(137,65,'_wp_attachment_backup_sizes','a:1:{s:9:\"full-orig\";a:3:{s:5:\"width\";i:358;s:6:\"height\";i:141;s:4:\"file\";s:11:\"support.jpg\";}}'),(149,68,'_edit_last','1'),(150,68,'_edit_lock','1540083456:1'),(151,68,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_dslc_staff_cats',''),(152,68,'dslc_staff_position','Manager/Web Designer'),(153,68,'dslc_staff_social_twitter',''),(154,68,'dslc_staff_social_instagram',''),(155,68,'dslc_staff_social_facebook',''),(156,68,'dslc_staff_social_googleplus',''),(157,68,'dslc_staff_social_linkedin',''),(158,68,'dslc_staff_social_email',''),(159,68,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(160,69,'_edit_last','1'),(161,69,'_edit_lock','1540083425:1'),(162,69,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_dslc_staff_cats',''),(170,69,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(171,70,'_edit_last','1'),(172,70,'_edit_lock','1540083704:1'),(173,70,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_dslc_projects_cats',''),(176,70,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','website'),(177,70,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','website'),(178,70,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','28'),(179,70,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(189,72,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(190,72,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(191,72,'_menu_item_object_id','25'),(192,72,'_menu_item_object','page'),(193,72,'_menu_item_target',''),(194,72,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(195,72,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(196,72,'_menu_item_url',''),(198,73,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(199,73,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(200,73,'_menu_item_object_id','19'),(201,73,'_menu_item_object','page'),(202,73,'_menu_item_target',''),(203,73,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(204,73,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(205,73,'_menu_item_url',''),(211,62,'_edit_lock','1499276448:1'),(212,62,'_wp_attachment_backup_sizes','a:1:{s:9:\"full-orig\";a:3:{s:5:\"width\";i:239;s:6:\"height\";i:211;s:4:\"file\";s:10:\"images.jpg\";}}'),(213,62,'_edit_last','1'),(214,62,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(217,74,'_wp_attached_file','2017/07/download-1.png'),(218,74,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:302;s:6:\"height\";i:183;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2017/07/download-1.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a: